pull.title: cli: fix Fatal LevelDB error when specifying -blockfilterindex=basic twice
pull.body: This PR fixes #17679 by replacing BlockFilterType-vector with a set of the same type to make sure that only unique filter types get inserted.

But that doesn't matter here as the `g_enabled_filter_types` is only getting iterated over once :smile:
